  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON : The proposal is considered to be harmful to the character and appearance of the adjoining main building and the wider conservation area.  The works provide a feature which on account of its scale and design including fenestration is considered unsympathetic to the surrounding architectural detailing and townscape.  The proposal in this regard is considered to be unacceptable and fails to comply with PPS5 Planning and the Historic Environment; policies 7.4, 7.6 and 7.8 of the London Plan 2011, policy CS9 of the Islington Core Strategy 2011; the objectives of policies D4 (Designing in Context), D11 (Extensions and Alterations) and D27 (Side Extensions) of the Islington Unitary Development Plan, the guidance of the Islington Urban Design Guide, and the guidance of the Arlington Square Conservation Area Design Guidelines."
